WEBVTT

00:03.847 --> 00:06.548
♪ Good morning, USA!

00:06.583 --> 00:10.452
♪ I got a feeling that it's
gonna be a wonderful day ♪

00:10.486 --> 00:13.422
♪ The sun in the sky
has a smile on his face ♪

00:13.456 --> 00:17.892
♪ And he's shining a salute
to the American race ♪

00:19.762 --> 00:22.930
♪ Oh, boy, it's swell to say

00:22.964 --> 00:25.132
♪ Good...
♪ Good morning, USA

00:25.166 --> 00:26.701
Aah!

00:27.969 --> 00:30.731
♪ Good morning, USA!

00:30.851 --> 00:37.288
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrections by honeybunny</font>
